code: @Override public void configure(SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactory factory, ConnectionFactory connectionFactory) {     PropertyMapper map = PropertyMapper.get().     RabbitProperties.SimpleContainer config = getRabbitProperties().getListener().getSimple().     configure(factory, connectionFactory, config).     map.from(config::getConcurrency).whenNonNull().to(factory::setConcurrentConsumers).     map.from(config::getMaxConcurrency).whenNonNull().to(factory::setMaxConcurrentConsumers).     map.from(config::getTransactionSize).whenNonNull().to(factory::setTxSize). }
